nglement, the\nnearest-neighbor information theoretic measures can be both ergodic as well as\nnon-ergodic, depending on the system parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 May 2016 18:33:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2017 15:07:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-10"}
