ing, and the Ryu-Takayanagi formula for the\nentanglement entropy appears naturally.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 May 2016 20:07:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Jul 2017 22:12:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-05"}
